{
  "enabled": true,
  "version": "1",
  "name": "sync-steering-docs",
  "description": "同步 Steering 场景文档和参考文档",
  "when": {
    "type": "userTriggered"
  },
  "then": {
    "type": "askAgent",
    "prompt": "Please synchronize Steering documentation:\n\n**Instructions**:\n1. Use context-gatherer subagent to read all scenario documents in .kiro/powers/gemini-fullstack/steering/\n2. Use context-gatherer subagent to read all reference documents in .kiro/docs/\n3. Analyze the summaries to check consistency between scenario docs and reference docs\n4. Update cross-references between documents using Desktop Commander MCP\n5. Verify all links are valid based on the gathered context\n6. Update CHANGELOG.md with changes using Desktop Commander MCP\n7. Ensure version numbers are consistent\n\n**Follow KIRO-RULES.md**: Never directly use readFile or readMultipleFiles. Always use context-gatherer subagent for reading documentation. Use Desktop Commander MCP for writing files.\n\nProvide a summary of changes made."
  }
}
